This game is brilliant. It's simple to understand and great to master. If you're skilled you can have fun dominating people in competitive play. If you're after a casual experience there are loads of mini-games to find tucked away in the community server browser. 

The people that play this game can be quite toxic at times but if you push past them you can find some fantastic people. Completely recommend.
